data.text:
What a thrilling day on the cricket field! During our friendly cricket match between the Compliance, Internal Audit, and Legal Affairs divisions, we witnessed some extraordinary talent and teamwork that truly made the event unforgettable. From strategic bowling to powerful batting, it was clear that we had some genuine cricket enthusiasts among us. The game was not just competitive but also filled with laughter that brought our teams closer together. Events like these not only showcase our skills beyond the office but also remind us of the importance of teamwork, sportsmanship, and having fun together. Sarwat Salahuddin | Ahsan Mohsin Shaikh | Jawad Ali | Hira Azhar, SHRM-CP #jazz #dunyakobataado #employeeengagement

Today, in the P&O division we had a blast with our very own Potluck Party! It was a feast of flavors as everyone brought their A-game and shared their homemade culinary delights. From savory to sweet, we had it all! It's incredible to see how talented our team is not just at the workplace but also in the kitchen. The variety of dishes was outstanding! These moments remind us why our workplace feels like a big family. #jazz #employeeengagement

What a smashing time we had in the P&O Division with our exhilarating Cricket Action! The enthusiasm displayed by each team member was truly remarkable. Check out this fantastic picture capturing the thrill of the game and the joy on our faces! Special thanks to everyone who participated and contributed to making this event an enjoyable experience. Together, we demonstrated the power of unity and the importance of fostering a positive work environment. #jazz #employeeengagement

Today’s town hall for our Finance division covered, business updates from our CFO and P&O highlights from the HR Business Partnership team. The session was closed by celebrating the outstanding achievements of our Divisional Champs for Q1 2023, we couldn't be prouder of their hard work and dedication. Each and every one of you has demonstrated exceptional talent, innovation, and perseverance. Congratulations on this well-deserved recognition! Gabor Kocsis | Zulqarnain Cheema | Aqueela Mumtaz | Fawad Haider | Khurram Akhlaque | Sheraz Ahmad Rana, CTP | Usman Qureshi | Atif Khan | Ali Raza Khan | Jawad Ali | Hira Azhar, SHRM-CP #jazz #divsionalchamps #townhall #employeerecognition #dunyakobatado

A huge round of applause and heartfelt appreciation to our outstanding Divisional Champs Mariam Ali | Waleed Khawar Ahmed | Mehvish Naseer Cheema (SHRM-CP) Mehak Irshad | Haseeb Ahmed | Maaz Farooqi in the People & Organization division for their remarkable performance in the Q1 2023! Your dedication, expertise, and unwavering commitment have made a significant impact. Jawad Ali | Sanam Sheikh | Farah Sheikh | Ayesha Pervaiz | Syed Usman A. | Hira Azhar, SHRM-CP #jazz #dunyakobatado #employeeappreciation #employeerecognition
